description: DAILY CHARME Self-Leveling Rubber Base Gel

Daily Charme Self-Leveling Rubber Base Gel creates a strong adhesive bond between the natural nail surface and gel polish. It's specially designed to smooth over unevenness of the natural nail surface. It also prevents gel polishes from lifting and protects the natural nails from possible stains.
1. Apply an even coat over your natural nail, wait for it to self-level to your liking. 2. Cure with LED lamp for 30 seconds, or UV lamp for 2 mins.
Polyurethane Acrylate Oligomers, Hydroxyethl Methacrylate, 2-Hydroxy-2methylpropiophenone, Triethylene Glycol Dimethacrylate, Hydroxy Cyclohexyl Phenyl Kestone Made in Taiwan
